title: How I Do Maintenance
itunes:title: How I Do Maintenance
description:
You've been asking for a maintenance podcast...here it is! In today's episode I talk about my journey to maintenance and how I STAY in maintenance.
 
I also teach today about how to KNOW when you're in maintenance and how to adapt your mindset from losing weight to keeping it off.
